Question: Switch the shipping carrier for order ID 8819 to 'FedEx'.
Call: { "func_call": "update_record", "table": "orders", "id": 8819, "data": { "delivery_method": "FedEx", "tracking_number": "FX123456789" }, "where": "id = 8819" }
